 rates hourly using an 8-hour TWAP of the premium between perpetual and index prices. The exchange's order book model on Sui enables fast settlement with funding payments processed automatically every hour. Bluefin's institutional-grade matching engine ensures precise rate calculations even during volatile Filecoin network events or storage market fluctuations."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
